      "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"http://www.dritare.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/favicon-32x32.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n      <a href=\"http://www.dritare.net/2017/09/10/tu-rrojne-bes-kallaket-se-hajria-iku/1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"09:01PM - 10 September 2017\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Dritare.net – 10 Sep 17</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/450;\"><img src=\"http://www.dritare.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/hajrie.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.dritare.net/2017/09/10/tu-rrojne-bes-kallaket-se-hajria-iku/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">T’u rrojnë Bes Kallakët, se Hajria iku!</a></h3>\n\n<p>Nga Ilir Levonja\nNuk e di pse shqiptarëve u dhimbset kaq shumë ikja e Hajrie Rondos? Kemi kaq kollozër tani, sa, mjafton një Kallak a një Fevzi, a Mamaq…, ku di unë tjetër. Ia kemi kaluar edhe Hollivudit. Koha e kinemasë së Hajries ishte një...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
